name: MeatBuds #2291
description: Who says you shouldn't play with your food? MeatBuds are the hottest new collectible comestible that you can grow at home! Simply hang the starter pouch in your pantry bay, connect the color-coded nutrient tubes to your wastepod (or "flavorpod" as we like to call it) and watch it grow before your eyes! In just 3 cycles, you'll have a tasty treat that can be enjoyed hot or cold. For your next meal, make it a MeatBud! Color and taste may vary. [Created in paintdotnet using assets from "Purposeful Vulnerability" by HeyHazmus and "Nimbuds" by Bryan Brinkman]
